# BuildKit uses this per-Dockerfile ignore file (named <Dockerfile>.dockerignore) for the
# `apify-mcp-evals:local` image build. Keeps the context small and correct: host node_modules
# (wrong-platform binaries) and build output are rebuilt inside the image.
.git
# Never bake secrets into the image.
.env*
**/.env*
*.pem
**/*.pem
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.venv
**/.venv
evals/workflows/harbor/tasks
evals/workflows/harbor/jobs
storage
apify_storage
crawlee_storage
.idea
.vscode
